    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a decent budget-friendly option for someone willing to put in a little work. The engine and transmission are functional, though you may notice some minor leaks and the ride isn't as smooth as a newer model. The exterior shows its age with several scratches, minor dents, and some paint fading on the hood. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and visible wear. While it is currently drivable, it will likely need some routine maintenance and minor repairs in the near future to keep it reliable.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
